      "bookmarkId": "3300029064_5_3996-4013",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3996-4013",
      "markText": "正是消费，而不是劳动，创造了价值。",
      "totalCount": 319,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029064&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3996&rangeEnd=4013",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3b432180813ab71dag0143b3?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3996&rangeEnd=4013"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029064_6_32623-32681",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "32623-32681",
      "markText": "如果允许婚礼花费不受约束地无限增长，那么市民家庭孩子的结婚时间只能延迟，甚至永远不能结婚，这将把社区送上灭亡的道路。",
      "totalCount": 162,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029064&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=32623&rangeEnd=32681",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3b432180813ab71dag0143b3?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=32623&rangeEnd=32681"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029064_13_27166-27219",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "27166-27219",
      "markText": "如果消费主义被定义为一种即时满足的文化，即个人消费驱动经济并主导日常生活，那么中国人根本就不是消费主义者。",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029064&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=27166&rangeEnd=27219",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3b432180813ab71dag0143b3?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=27166&rangeEnd=27219"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029064_5_9524-9602",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "9524-9602",
      "markText": "本书关注的是两个进程之间的相互作用：一个进程是，随着时间推移，各种制度和观念是如何塑造消费的；另一个进程是，消费是如何反过来改造权力、社会关系和价值体系的。",
      "totalCount": 153,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029064&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9524&rangeEnd=9602",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3b432180813ab71dag0143b3?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=9524&rangeEnd=9602"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029064_5_8733-8754",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "8733-8754",
      "markText": "人们通过自己的私人物品发现自己，表达自己。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029064&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=8733&rangeEnd=8754",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3b432180813ab71dag0143b3?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=8733&rangeEnd=8754"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029064_5_7833-7881",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "7833-7881",
      "markText": "有些人希望，可供选择的商品和服务增加，会弱化旧有的阶级和品位等级制度，培育出一个更多元化的社会。",
      "totalCount": 110,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029064&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7833&rangeEnd=7881",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3b432180813ab71dag0143b3?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7833&rangeEnd=7881"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029064_12_27105-27164",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "27105-27164",
      "markText": "丰裕使美国人变得更特别，而使欧洲人变得更普通。在美国，你要么读很多书，要么根本不读；你要么做很多运动，要么一点都不做。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029064&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=27105&rangeEnd=27164",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3b432180813ab71dag0143b3?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=27105&rangeEnd=27164"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029064_6_20329-20397",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "20329-20397",
      "markText": "奢侈消费是为子孙后代服务的，是为了将家族的名字铭刻在城市世世代代的史册上。文艺复兴时期的公民人文主义偏爱稳固的东西。花钱是为了获得永恒。",
      "totalCount": 99,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029064&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=20329&rangeEnd=20397",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3b432180813ab71dag0143b3?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=20329&rangeEnd=20397"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029064_8_13822-13902",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "13822-13902",
      "markText": "联合抵制购买奴隶种植的蔗糖发展成了一项跨大西洋的大规模运动。妇女站在最前沿，利用她们对钱包的控制、家庭美德观念以及她们被频频提及的同情能力。伦理消费主义诞生了。",
      "totalCount": 98,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029064&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=13822&rangeEnd=13902",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3b432180813ab71dag0143b3?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=13822&rangeEnd=13902"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029064_5_1824-1876",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1824-1876",
      "markText": "在发达国家，而且在发展中国家也越来越如此，身份、政治、经济和环境在很大程度上是被“我们如何消费”塑造的。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029064&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1824&rangeEnd=1876",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3b432180813ab71dag0143b3?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1824&rangeEnd=1876"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029064_7_41911-41934",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "41911-41934",
      "markText": "她渴求的东西越多，她自己就越发沦落为一件商品。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300029064&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=41911&rangeEnd=41934",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3b432180813ab71dag0143b3?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=41911&rangeEnd=41934"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300029064_5_4038-4113",
